Despite Barkley's impressive statistics, some analysts believe that the MVP debate is unproductive. Meanwhile, Barkley has expressed his gratitude for his teammates' contributions to his success, particularly in the absence of Brandon Graham, who suffered an injury during the game. Barkley also extended his well wishes to former teammate Daniel Jones, who was recently released by the Giants, hoping that he finds success with a new team.
